{{Transcript|event}}
{{transcript list|Patty Seer|Cook (Lumbridge)|Warmhandz|Bob|Party Pete|Archmage Sedridor|Thurgo|General Bentnoze}}

==Before starting the event==
===Warmhandz===
* '''Warmhandz:''' Me not interested in talking.
* {{tact|end}}

===Party Pete===
* {{tselect|What would you like to talk about?}}
* {{topt|Birthday Event 2023}}
** '''Party Pete:''' Oh it's very exciting, the Cake Off, but you should try talking to Patty Seer in Lumbridge to get involved!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Something else.}}

===Trying to take the gnome cake, varrock cake, goblin cake, or dwarf cake before starting the event===
* '''Player:''' I probably shouldn't touch this for now.
* {{tact|end}}

==Baking Troubles==
===Talking to Patty Seer===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Oh no... what do I do?
* '''Patty Seer:''' It's all gone wrong...
* '''Player:''' What's wrong?
* '''Patty Seer:''' I'm supposed to be cooking a cake for the Cake Off but my prized tin has broken!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What's the Cake Off?}}
** '''Player:''' What's the Cake Off?
** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh, you don't know about the Great Gielinor Cake Off? It's Party Pete's newest idea!
** '''Patty Seer:''' He's invited representatives from across the world to have their baking skills judged.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Who are you?}}
** '''Player:''' Who are you?
** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh! I'm Patty Seer, a wandering cook! I'm traveling the world learning everything I can about food.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Your prized tin?}}
** '''Player:''' Your prized tin?
** '''Patty Seer:''' Yes, I use it for every cake I bake. It brings me luck.
** '''Player:''' What's happened to it?
** '''Patty Seer:''' I'm not sure how, but it's broken in two... Do you think you might be able to help me?
** {{tselect|Start the 2023 Birthday Event?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm sure I can find someone to fix it!
*** {{tcond|If the player does not have inventory space:}}
**** {{tbox|You don't have enough inventory space to start this event. Please free up at least 2 slots.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Cracked cake tin detail.png|Patty hands you the broken cake tin.}}
*** '''Cook:''' What about Bob?
*** '''Player:''' Do you think he can fix it?
*** '''Cook:''' Yes, I'd imagine he can! Not to mention, he owes me one!
*** '''Cook:''' Take this to him, it should cover the cost of the repair. You should be able to find him in his shop to the south.
*** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
**** '''Cook:''' Oh! You can't hold this right now, I'll give it to Patty for safekeeping!
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Promissory note (2023 Birthday event) detail.png|The cook hands you a promissory note.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No}}
*** '''Player:''' I don't think I can help right now.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I don't think I can help right now...}}
** '''Player:''' I don't think I can help right now.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Patty after declining to start===
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What's the Cake Off?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Who are you?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Your prized tin?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|I don't think I can help right now...}}
** {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Patty after getting the Cracked cake tin before getting the Promissory note===
* '''Cook:''' What about Bob?
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Patty after the Chef fails to give the promissory note===
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Cracked cake tin:}}
** {{tact|(Same as reclaiming dialogue below.)}}
* '''Player:''' Could I have that note the cook mentioned?
* '''Patty Seer:''' Of course!
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tbox|pic=Promissory note (2023 Birthday event) detail.png|Patty hands you the promissory note.}}
* '''Patty Seer:''' There you go! Try not to lose it!
* {{tact|end}}

===Using any item on Patty, including [[chef's hat]]===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Oh... thank you for the offer but I'm not interested in that.
* {{tact|end}}

===Reclaiming lost items from Patty===
* {{tcond|If the player lost both the cake tin and promissory note:}}
** '''Player:''' I've managed to lose both the cake tin and the note you gave me.
** '''Patty Seer:''' No worries, I managed to recover both of them. Try not to lose them again.
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh, you don't have enough space to hold them both right now. Come talk to me when you've got more space in your inventory.
*** {{tact|end}}
** '''Player:''' Thanks, I'll try my best to keep a hold on them.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tact|If the player lost the promissory note:}}
** '''Player:''' I've lost the promissory note the cook gave me.
** '''Patty Seer:''' No worries, I found it floating in the wind.
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh, you don't have enough space to hold it right now. I'll keep it here for you when you're ready.
*** {{tact|end}}
** '''Patty Seer:''' Please try not to lose it again.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tact|If the player lost the cake tin:}}
** '''Player:''' I've lost your cake tin.
** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh! This cake tin? I found it lying on the ground.
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** '''Patty Seer:''' Please don't lose it again!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Cook===
* {{tselect|What would you like to talk about?}}
* {{topt|Birthday Event 2023}}
** '''Player:''' Can we talk about the current event?
** '''Cook:''' Patty is likely to know more than me, try chatting to her!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Something else.}}

===Talking to Patty after getting the promissory note===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Have you spoken to Bob yet?
* '''Player:''' No, not yet.
* {{tact|end}}

===Using cracked cake tin or promissory note on Patty===
* '''Patty Seer:''' I can't do much with these, try taking them to Bob.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Bob===
* {{tselect|What would you like to talk about?}}
* {{topt|The Birthday Event 2023}}
** {{tcond|If the player lost the cracked cake tin:}}
*** '''Bob:''' I'm not sure we have anything to discuss on that, can I help with anything else?
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|event=No|Give me a quest!}}
*** {{topt|event=No|Have you anything to sell?}}
*** {{topt|event=No|Can you repair my items for me?}}
** '''Player:''' Could you fix this tin for me?
** {{tbox|pic=Cracked cake tin detail.png|You show the tin to Bob.}}
** '''Bob:''' I could. It will be expensive though.
** {{tcond|If the player lost the promissory note:}}
*** '''Player:''' I did have an IOU from the Cook... Where did I put it?
*** '''Bob:''' I can't help you out without seeing it first unfortunately.
*** {{tact|end}}
** '''Player:''' The cook mentioned that you owe him a favour.
** '''Bob:''' I'd hoped he'd have forgotten that by now...
** '''Player:''' He gave me this note and said it would cover the cost.
** {{tbox|pic=Promissory note (2023 Birthday event) detail.png|You show the note to Bob.}}
** '''Bob:''' Yes, that should do it... Hand that tin over here then.
** {{tbox|Bob takes the tin and begins to hammer it back into shape...}}
** {{tbox|And offers you a completed cake tin!}}
** '''Bob:''' There you go, as good as new. There's just something great about Lumbridge tin.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Something else.}}

===Using promissory note on Bob without the cracked cake tin===
* '''Bob:''' I'm not sure we have anything to discuss on that, can I help with anything else?
* '''Bob:''' Sorry friend, but I can't do anything with that.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Patty after giving Bob the cracked cake tin===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Any luck with Bob?
* '''Player:''' Yes, I've left the tin with him for finishing!
* '''Patty Seer:''' Great! He'll probably be done by now though, so you might want to pick it up!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Bob after giving him the cracked cake tin before getting the fixed cake tin===
* {{tselect|What would you like to talk about?}}
* {{topt|The Birthday Event 2023}}
** '''Bob:''' I finished repairing that cake tin for you!
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Prized cake tin detail.png|Bob hands you back a repaired cake tin.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Something else.}}

===Talking to Patty after losing the prized cake tin===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Was Bob able to repair the tin?
* '''Player:''' He said he would be able to.
* '''Patty Seer:''' Did you remember to bring it back with you?
* '''Player:''' Ah.
* {{tact|end}}

====Reclaiming a lost prized cake tin====
* '''Player:''' I've lost Patty's cake tin.
* '''Bob:''' Luckily for you I have another tin you can give her.
* '''Player:''' But won't she notice that this isn't her lucky one?
* '''Bob:''' She won't if you don't tell her. The original wasn't anything particularly special.
* '''Player:''' So, why wouldn't she just replace it?
* '''Bob:''' You'd have to ask her that yourself.
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** '''Bob:''' I'm not sure we have anything to discuss on that, can I help with anything else?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|event=No|Give me a quest!}}
** {{topt|event=No|Have you anything to sell?}}
** {{topt|event=No|Can you repair my items for me?}}
* {{tbox|pic=Prized cake tin detail.png|Bob hands you the new cake tin.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Returning the tin===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Was Bob able to repair the tin?
* '''Player:''' Yes! He did it without too much trouble!
* {{tbox|pic=Prized cake tin detail.png|You hand the repaired tin over to Patty.}}
* '''Patty Seer:''' Oh it looks brand new! Now, is there a chance you may be able to help find my hat?
* '''Player:''' Your hat?
* '''Patty Seer:''' Yes, my lucky hat... it was stolen by a goblin. It can't have gotten very far by now!
* '''Player:''' Why would a goblin want to steal your hat?
* '''Patty Seer:''' I'm not sure... could you chase it down to find out?
* '''Player:''' Of course!
* '''Patty Seer:''' Try near the general store, I heard there was a goblin lurking there.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Patty after giving her the prized cake tin===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Any luck finding the goblin that stole my hat yet?
* '''Player:''' Not yet!
* '''Patty Seer:''' They can't have gone far, they'll probably be wearing the hat!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Warmhandz===
* '''Player:''' Hello there, that's a nice hat you've got.
* '''Warmhandz:''' Yes, it my cooking hat.
* '''Player:''' Where did you get it?
* '''Warmhandz:''' Found it in the castle. Fit my head perfectly!
* '''Player:''' It may do, but I need to return it to its owner.
* '''Warmhandz:''' Without hat, I not chef. Watch for ten years how to cook in castle, now my turn.
* '''Player:''' I may have an idea... Why don't you go and talk to Patty Seer in the castle. She could help you be a chef.
* '''Warmhandz:''' You think she help?
* '''Player:''' Of course! She would probably love to learn about goblin cuisine from you.
* {{tbox|The goblin stares at you, trying to process your words.}}
* '''Player:''' Things like food and drinks.
* '''Warmhandz:''' She learn... from me.
* {{tbox|The goblin starts to move quickly towards the castle.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Patty or Warmhandz in the castle===
* '''Patty Seer:''' So you're the one that took my hat, are you?
* '''Warmhandz:''' Yes, need it to be chef.
* '''Patty Seer:''' You... need it? To be a chef? That's absurd. Anyone can be a chef if they want to be!
* '''Warmhandz:''' No... chef hat, always!
* '''Patty Seer:''' Well, I suppose I can let you keep that! It's always brought me luck!
* '''Warmhandz:''' I keep. Lucky Warmhandz!
* '''Patty Seer:''' Of course, you know what every chef does need to do?
* '''Warmhandz:''' Wear hat.
* '''Patty Seer:''' Well, yes, but what else?
* '''Warmhandz:''' Cook. Warmhandz can cook!
* '''Patty Seer:''' Warmhandz can indeed cook.
* {{tbox|The two begin to talk about baking a cake for the Cake Off.}}
* {{tbox|A significant amount of mess and noise later...}}
* '''Patty Seer:''' Wow, that looks incredible!
* '''Warmhandz:''' I learn ten years from watching cook, and have lucky hat.
* '''Patty Seer:''' You've clearly learned a lot in that time.
* '''Warmhandz:''' Watching not good like doing.
* '''Patty Seer:''' So [player name], what do you think?
* {{tbox|pic=Special cake detail.png|Patty shows you the cake the two baked.}}
* '''Player:''' That is a good looking cake! Is it ready to go to the Cake Off?
* '''Patty Seer:''' I think so! It needs to be delivered to Party Pete in Falador. Would you mind taking it to him?
* '''Player:''' I'd be happy to!
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player is on a normal world:}}
** '''Patty Seer:''' I can offer you a one time teleport to the Party Room if you would like?
** {{tselect|Would you like to teleport to the Party Room?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** '''Player:''' That would be useful, thanks.
*** '''Patty Seer:''' Remember, this needs to get to Party Pete. I'll get you as close as possible, but this is an imprecise art.
*** '''Player:''' Imprecise?
*** '''Patty Seer:''' Don't worry! I've done this before... Once or twice.
*** {{tact|(The player is teleported to the Falador Party Room.)}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm okay for the moment, thank you.
*** '''Patty Seer:''' Okay, feel free to come back to me when you're ready to head to Falador!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player is on a [[Quest Speedrunning]] world:}}
** '''Patty Seer:''' Best of luck in the judging!
** {{tbox|Patty would offer you a teleport to Falador on a regular world. It is not available on this type of world.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Patty before getting the special cake===
* '''Patty Seer:''' Right, have you got the space to take this cake to Pete?
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** '''Player:''' No, I don't think I do.
** {{tact|end}}
* '''Player:''' Yes I do!
* '''Patty Seer:''' I can offer you a one time teleport to the Party Room if you would like?
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Patty after not accepting the teleport before starting the Cake Off===
* '''Patty Seer:''' I can offer you a one time teleport to the Party Room if you would like?
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Patty after losing the special cake===
* '''Player:''' I seem to have lost track of that cake you baked.
* '''Patty Seer:''' Well, thankfully it's a fairly simple recipe!
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** '''Patty Seer:''' Oh, you don't have enough space to hold one right now, I'll make it when you have room.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tbox|Patty hands you a near perfect replica of the cake.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Warmhandz before going to Falador===
* {{tbox|Warmhandz is happily talking to themselves about baking a cake.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Visiting the Falador Party Room==
===Talking to Patty after using the one-time teleport===
* '''Patty Seer:''' I'm afraid I can't teleport you to Falador again, so you'll have to deliver that cake by yourself.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Archmage Sedridor before delivering the cake===
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' I'm very glad Pete didn't ask us to bake a cake... Mixing wizards and baking is a recipe for disaster!
* {{tact|end}}

===Gnome child===
* '''Gnome child:''' I have reinvented the meaning of a cake. Observe the exceptional textures of the crunchy.
* '''Player:''' Oh. Okay... I think I can see them?
* '''Gnome child:''' Excellent.
* {{tact|end}}

====Checking the Gnome cake====
* {{tbox|pic=Gnome cake detail.png|It's the Gnome Child's entry to the Cake Off. It's not really a cake.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===King Roald===
* '''King Roald:''' I'm very proud of this cake... Even if it accidentally rolled back into the oven!
* '''Player:''' It looks entirely burnt! Was there no time to make another one?
* '''King Roald:''' I've no idea what you mean! It seems perfectly edible.
* {{tact|end}}

====Checking the Varrock cake====
* {{tbox|pic=Varrock cake detail.png|It's Varrock's entry to the Cake Off. It's been burned.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===General Wartface===
* '''General Wartface:''' Cake should be green! Green good!
* {{tact|end}}

===General Bentnoze===
* '''General Bentnoze:''' Cake should be red! Big High War God say so!
* {{tact|end}}

====Checking the Goblin cake====
* {{tbox|pic=Goblin cake detail.png|It's the Goblin entry to the Cake Off. It looks like it's made from chocolate. It probably isn't.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Thurgo===
* '''Thurgo:''' This is an Imcando favourite, cooked to perfection.
* '''Player:''' It looks like a pie?
* '''Thurgo:''' Yes! It's a redberry pie! Have you ever eaten one before?
* '''Player:''' Oh I can't remember! I'm sure it's delicious!
* {{tact|end}}

====Checking the Dwarf cake====
* {{tbox|pic=Dwarf cake detail.png|It's the Dwarf entry to the Cake Off. It looks a lot more like a pie than anything. Perhaps it's an illusion cake.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Delivering the Cake==
===Talking to Party Pete===
* {{tselect|What would you like to talk about?}}
* {{topt|Birthday Event 2023}}
** '''Player:''' Pete! I have Lumbridge's entry to the Cake Off here.
** {{tcond|If the player lost the cake:}}
*** '''Party Pete:''' Oh good, that's the last one I was waiting on! Hand it over.
*** {{tbox|You search all of your available pockets, finding no trace of the Lumbridge cake.}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh, I'm sure I had it just a second ago. I'll track it down!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Special cake detail.png|You show Pete the cake.}}
** '''Party Pete:''' Oh, that's perfect! Just in time for the judging too.
** '''Player:''' Great, and don't mind the goblin, they're one of the chefs.
** '''Party Pete:''' Oh lovely! Now there's a couple of things I need to know about this cake.
** '''Player:''' Such as?
** '''Party Pete:''' Firstly, was anything inedible baked into it?
** '''Player:''' I don't believe so, no.
** {{tbox|Pete notes down information about the cake on a small card.}}
** '''Party Pete:''' Secondly, may I hold onto it until the judging is over?
** '''Player:''' Of course.
** {{tbox|pic=Special cake detail.png|You hand the cake over to Pete.}}
** '''Party Pete:''' Now then, I could use your help with sorting out a slight problem.
** '''Player:''' Oh?
** '''Party Pete:''' Sedridor over there has had some trouble with the everlasting candle. He can't get it to light.
** '''Player:''' Well, that's certainly one way to make it last forever.
** '''Party Pete:''' Unfortunately, an unlit candle is not entirely... celebratory.
** '''Player:''' Do you want me to ask him what the problem is?
** '''Party Pete:''' If you wouldn't mind?
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Something Else}}

