==The Great Gielinor Cake Off==
* {{qact|As the cutscene begins, [[The Trade Parade]] plays.}}
* '''Party Pete:''' Welcome everyone to the inaugural Great Gielinor Cake Off! The cakes are ready, and I hope you are too ScryNet viewers!
* '''Party Pete:''' We've got five cakes to judge today, so let's get right into it!
* '''Party Pete:''' First up, we have Thurgo and his Imcando Dwarf Cake! Or... Is it more of a pie?
* {{tbox|Pete takes a bite of the Dwarf Cake, before taking a moment to think.}}
* '''Party Pete:''' It's definitely a pie, but it is delicious!
* '''Thurgo:''' I'm glad you like it, I can give you the recipe if you want?
* '''Party Pete:''' That's very kind, but... Could it not have been a cake?
* '''Thurgo:''' No, it's important that it remains as a pie.
* '''Party Pete:''' Next up, the Goblin cake from Bentnoze and Wartface! On first appearances, it looks good. Rich and chocolatey.
* '''Party Pete:''' Hmm. That doesn't taste like chocolate... What is it?
* '''General Bentnoze:''' Is mud.
* '''Party Pete:''' Mud?
* '''General Bentnoze:''' Mud.
* {{qact|Pete performs the [[panic]] emote.}}
* '''Party Pete:''' Okay. Moving on swiftly to...
* {{tbox|The loud beating of wings can be heard over Pete's voice.}}
* {{qact|The camera pans to [[Elvarg]] at the entrance, or [[Alvarg]] if the player completed [[Dragon Slayer I]]. The camera then pans back to Pete.}}
* '''Party Pete:''' A dragon? Look out!
* '''Party Pete:''' Quick, cut the feed.
